-- ds.page.body:

Sometimes we want to display a search bar in blog home page. Our
`blog-template-1` search-card feature helps you to create search card.

It's very simple to create your search bar using `-- ds.search-card` which
can be added inside `-- ds.page`.

-- ds.h2: Example:

-- ds.rendered:

-- ds.rendered.input:

\-- ds.search-card: Subscribe
help-info: Sign up in 2 minutes

-- ds.rendered.output:

-- ds.search-card: Subscribe
help-info: Sign up in 2 minutes

-- end: ds.rendered.output

-- end: ds.rendered

-- ds.h3: Let's understand above code snippet:

-- collapse.collapse: `-- ds.search-card:`
remove-gap: true

Its blog-template-1 default search-card component.

